(127,85,5,'Two Connected Pawns','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">The further the pawns are advanced, the easier it will be to win. If both connected pawns are two squares away from promoting (6th rank for white, 3rd for black) and the pawns don\'t include a rook pawn, one of the pawns will get promoted.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In the example below, after Kd5, black loses because of zugzwang. Because the pawns are on the 6th rank, the black bishop has no waiting moves.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":3,\"type\":\"chess-lesson\",\"content\":{\"position\":\"4kb2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/4K3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/5B2 w - - 0 1\",\"rotate\":false,\"chessState\":{\"moveHistory\":[{\"fen\":\"4kb2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/4K3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/5B2 w - - 0 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"4kb2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/1B2K3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8 b - - 1 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[62,26],\"checkSquare\":5,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"17117480-162e-11ed-99b3-a5a705317de8\",\"firstSquare\":62,\"secondSquare\":26,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"engine\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"3k1b2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/1B2K3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8 w - - 2 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[5,4],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"19f644f0-162e-11ed-99b3-a5a705317de8\",\"firstSquare\":5,\"secondSquare\":4,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"3k1b2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/1B1K4\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8 b - - 3 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[29,28],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"1b259d30-162e-11ed-99b3-a5a705317de8\",\"firstSquare\":29,\"secondSquare\":28,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"engine\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"2k2b2\\/8\\/3PP3\\/1B1K4\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8 w - - 4 3\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[4,3],\"checkSqua