(151,101,2,'Checkmates with Knight','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">If the defender\'s king is in the corner and can\'t escape, it\'s possible to checkmate even with one knight.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In the position below, the black king can\'t escape the corner. When it\'s black to move, and the black king is on a1, the knight must be ready to jump to b3 to deliver the checkmate in case black pushes the pawn.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":3,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">The goal for white is to reach c1 with the knight when the opponent\'s king is on a1, and it\'s black\'s turn to move. Black must push the pawn, and the checkmate is inevitable.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":4,\"type\":\"chess-lesson\",\"content\":{\"position\":\"8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/1K6\\/p7\\/k2N4\\/8 w - - 0 1\",\"chessState\":{\"moveHistory\":[{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/1K6\\/p7\\/k2N4\\/8 w - - 0 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/p1K5\\/k2N4\\/8 b - - 1 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[34,43],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"d40a5650-1b34-11ed-9b00-bb2875c3ef67\",\"firstSquare\":34,\"secondSquare\":43,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[{\"square\":42,\"color\":\"#F46120\"},{\"square\":50,\"color\":\"#F46120\"},{\"square\":58,\"color\":\"#F46120\"}],\"toMove\":\"engine\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/p1K5\\/3N4\\/k7 w - - 2 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[49,57],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"d6e40330-1b34-11ed-9b00-bb2875c3ef67\",\"firstSquare\":49,\"secondSquare\":57,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/p7\\/2KN4\\/k7 b - - 3 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[43,51],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[],\"highlighte