(199,127,1,'Rook vs. Knight','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In some positions in the rook vs. knight endgames, the side with the rook can force the checkmate. But in most cases, the knight will draw against the rook if the defender makes the right moves.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p>In this lesson, you will learn how to:<\\/p><ol start=\\\"1\\\" class=\\\"mb-2\\\"><li>Evaluate rook vs. knight endgames.<\\/li><li>Force the checkmate with the rook (when possible).<\\/li><li>Secure the draw with the knight (when possible).<\\/li><\\/ol>\"},{\"number\":3,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">Let\'s get started.<\\/p>\"}]','2022-10-15 00:00:00','2023-01-30 16:19:23'),
(200,127,2,'Cases when the knight can secure the draw','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In some positions in the rook vs. knight endgames, the side with the rook can force the checkmate. But in most cases, the knight will draw against the rook if the defender makes the right moves.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">As a defender, keep your king and knight close to each other and away from the board edge.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":3,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In the example below, white can\'t make any progress, and the draw is simple.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":4,\"type\":\"chess-lesson\",\"content\":{\"position\":\"8\\/4K3\\/8\\/2k1n3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/3R4 w - - 0 1\",\"chessState\":{\"moveHistory\":[{\"fen\":\"8\\/4K3\\/8\\/2k1n3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/3R4 w - - 0 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/4K3\\/2k1n3\\/8\\/8\\/8\\/3R4 b - - 1 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[13,21],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"0c240b70-4caf-11ed-b023-8ff1e76af223\",\"firstSquare\":13,\"secondSquare\":21,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"},{\"id\":\"1e13b830-4caf-11ed-b023-8ff1e76af223\",\"firstSquare\":21,\"secondSquare\":29,\"color\":\"#F46120\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"engine\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/4K3\\/2k5\\/2n5\\/8\\/8\\/3R4 w - - 2 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[29,35],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"0d1ac780-4caf-11ed-b023-8ff1e76af223\",\"firstSquare\":29,\"secondSquare\":35,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/4K3\\/2kR4\\/2n5\\/8\\/8\\/8 b - - 3 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[60,28],\"checkSquare\":27,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"0f5c2c00-4caf-11ed-b023-8ff1e76af223\",\"firstSquare\":60,\"secondSquare\":28,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSq