(216,137,1,'Queen vs. Queen and Pawn','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">The queen is the most powerful piece. Therefore, queen endgames are very complicated.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In this lesson, you will learn principles to help you find the right moves in complex positions. Let\'s get started.<\\/p>\"}]','2022-10-25 00:00:00','2023-01-30 16:19:23'),
(217,137,2,'When you\'re the attacker','[{\"number\":1,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">When you have the pawn advantage:<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":2,\"type\":\"warning\",\"content\":\"<ol><li>Avoid perpetual checks.<\\/li><li>Don\'t put your king in front of your pawn.<\\/li><\\/ol>\"},{\"number\":3,\"type\":\"info\",\"content\":\"<ol><li>Position your king on the same or adjacent file or rank as the defender\'s king.<\\/li><li>Your queen is placed best in the center.<\\/li><li>The farther your pawn is advanced, the greater the winning chances. When possible, advance the pawn.<\\/li><\\/ol>\"},{\"number\":4,\"type\":\"html\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"mb-2\\\">In the example below, white has a winning advantage. First, white must unblock the pawn (the king is blocking his pawn) and try to avoid possible checks to push the pawn forward. Usually, the attacker\'s king should move the king toward the opponent\'s queen to avoid checks.<\\/p>\"},{\"number\":5,\"type\":\"chess-lesson\",\"content\":{\"position\":\"8\\/3K4\\/3P4\\/3Q4\\/1q6\\/8\\/4k3\\/8 w - - 0 1\",\"rotate\":false,\"chessState\":{\"moveHistory\":[{\"fen\":\"8\\/3K4\\/3P4\\/3Q4\\/1q6\\/8\\/4k3\\/8 w - - 0 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/2KP4\\/3Q4\\/1q6\\/8\\/4k3\\/8 b - - 1 1\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[12,19],\"checkSquare\":null,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"54047f60-5493-11ed-a4f0-df40096507eb\",\"firstSquare\":12,\"secondSquare\":19,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"engine\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/2KP4\\/3Q4\\/8\\/2q5\\/4k3\\/8 w - - 2 2\",\"sound\":\"move\",\"lastMoves\":[34,43],\"checkSquare\":19,\"arrows\":[{\"id\":\"5617cf00-5493-11ed-a4f0-df40096507eb\",\"firstSquare\":34,\"secondSquare\":43,\"color\":\"#EFB701\"}],\"highlightedSquares\":[],\"toMove\":\"player\",\"newMove\":false},{\"fen\":\"8\\/8\\/3P4\\/1K1Q4